<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 06:15:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国的政策困境：信贷提振是否会导致通货紧缩？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-policy-dilemma-is-boosting-credit-deflationary-2024-01-10/</link><description>中国央行在消除通货紧缩威胁方面面临着一个重大障碍：更多的信贷流向生产力而非消费，暴露了经济的结构性缺陷并降低了货币政策工具的有效性。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 06:05:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-policy-dilemma-is-boosting-credit-deflationary-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>红海袭击：零售商急于避免春季系列产品延误</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/retailers-rush-avoid-delays-spring-collections-due-red-sea-attacks-2024-01-10/</link><description>高管和专家告诉路透社，世界各地的零售商都在中国农历新年假期前备货，并寻求通过红海运输的航空或铁路替代方案，以避免今年春天货架空空。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 06:04:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/retailers-rush-avoid-delays-spring-collections-due-red-sea-attacks-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>习近平向艾奥瓦州老朋友表示世界需要中美关系稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/old-friend-iowa-xi-says-world-requires-stability-china-us-ties-2024-01-10/</link><description>据中国官方媒体周三报道，中国国家主席习近平最近在回信一位爱荷华州人的来信中表示，世界的未来需要中美关系的稳定。他与爱荷华州人在近四十年前首次会面。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 05:57:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/old-friend-iowa-xi-says-world-requires-stability-china-us-ties-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>随着全球贸易回暖，中国12月出口有所改善</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-seen-improving-december-global-trade-picks-up-2024-01-10/</link><description>路透调查显示，中国出口可能在 12 月份连续第二个月增长更快，这进一步表明，由于电子行业的好转以及 2024 年借贷成本下降的预期，全球贸易开始复苏。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 05:13:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-seen-improving-december-global-trade-picks-up-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>印度尼西亚和菲律宾讨论南海事态发展 - 马科斯</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-philippines-discuss-south-china-sea-developments-marcos-2024-01-10/</link><description>菲律宾和印度尼西亚领导人周三会面，讨论一系列地区问题，包括南海的事态发展以及东南亚集团成员国之间更密切的合作。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 03:59:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-philippines-discuss-south-china-sea-developments-marcos-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>台湾选举前台湾与中国关系的关键事实</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/key-facts-taiwan-china-relations-ahead-taiwan-elections-2024-01-10/</link><description>台湾周六将举行投票选举新总统和国会。尽管台湾政府反对，中国仍将台湾视为中国的一个省及其领土的一部分，因此将密切关注这一结果。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 03:29:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/key-facts-taiwan-china-relations-ahead-taiwan-elections-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>台湾将在中国所谓的“和平与战争”选举中投票</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-vote-what-china-calls-peace-war-election-2024-01-10/</link><description>在日益自信的中国的阴影下，台湾周六将举行投票选举新总统和议会，中国称此次投票是和平与战争之间的选择。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 03:05:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-vote-what-china-calls-peace-war-election-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>美中在华盛顿结束为期两天的军事会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-china-conclude-two-days-military-talks-washington-2024-01-09/</link><description>五角大楼表示，美国和中国周二在华盛顿结束了为期两天的军事会谈，这是两国同意恢复军事关系以来的最新接触。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 23:41:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-china-conclude-two-days-military-talks-washington-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国卫星发射引发台湾大选前政治风暴</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-does-not-consider-china-satellite-launch-election-interference-2024-01-09/</link><description>周三，中国发射的一颗卫星飞越台湾，引发了错误的空袭警报，在台湾引发了一场关于中国动机的政治风暴，距离总统选举只有几天了。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 23:25:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-does-not-consider-china-satellite-launch-election-interference-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>哥谭市报告后，格里福斯将于周二下午召开董事会会议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/grifols-hold-board-meeting-tuesday-afternoon-after-gotham-city-report-2024-01-09/</link><description>西班牙制药公司 Grifols 董事会成员托马斯·达加 (Tomas Daga) 告诉路透社，该公司定于周二下午召开董事会会议，以回应 Gotham City Research 质疑该公司早些时候发布的会计报告的报告。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 11:24:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/grifols-hold-board-meeting-tuesday-afternoon-after-gotham-city-report-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国集团：2023年中国可能取代日本成为全球最大汽车出口国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-likely-dethroned-japan-worlds-top-auto-exporter-2023-china-group-2024-01-09/</link><description>中国乘用车协会(CPCA)周二表示，随着比亚迪、奇瑞等国内汽车制造商在海外取得重大进展，中国预计将在2023年超过日本成为全球最大的汽车出口国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 11:11:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-likely-dethroned-japan-worlds-top-auto-exporter-2023-china-group-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国汽车品牌通过电动汽车升级提高盈利能力-瑞银</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-auto-brands-improve-profitability-with-ev-upgrades-ubs-2024-01-09/</link><description>瑞银分析师周二表示，尽管全球最大汽车市场的竞争加剧，但由于中国汽车品牌不断升级电动汽车（EV）产品组合，中国汽车品牌预计将在 2024 年实现更好的盈利能力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 09:57:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-auto-brands-improve-profitability-with-ev-upgrades-ubs-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国卫星发射在关键投票前引发台湾攻击警报</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-alert-says-chinese-satellite-flies-over-south-taiwan-airspace-2024-01-09/</link><description>台湾政府周二发布空袭警报，称一枚携带卫星的中国火箭飞越台湾南部领空，台湾外交部长称这是关键选举前几天骚扰行为的一部分。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 07:50:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-alert-says-chinese-satellite-flies-over-south-taiwan-airspace-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>哥谭市会计查询使 Grifols 价值损失 38.3 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/short-seller-gotham-city-questions-grifols-debt-ratios-2024-01-09/</link><description>在对冲基金 Gotham City Research 对其会计提出质疑后，Grifols 股价周二下跌 30%，市值蒸发近 30 亿美元，促使这家西班牙制药商“断然”否认有任何不当行为。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 07:22:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/short-seller-gotham-city-questions-grifols-debt-ratios-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>桥梁困境凸显台湾选举中对中国的分歧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/bridge-dilemma-captures-divide-over-china-taiwan-elections-2024-01-09/</link><description>陈沧江指着办公室一水之隔的厦门摩天大楼，回忆起30年前这座中国南方城市和台湾金门岛一样低矮的情况。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 07:18:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/bridge-dilemma-captures-divide-over-china-taiwan-elections-2024-01-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>